004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T20:55:03.000Z","msg":"外賣先仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd飯未熟<br />\n好多外賣仔都係呀差做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n$125蚊 我俾$140 佢諗都無諗過找錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nM記d人點會咁 <br />\n通常都係找錢先俾tips架啦"},{"pid":"99d982f0f0ba3d7401dcda57811b2cc5150e1ddc","tid":444461,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:00:41.000Z","msg":"其實炸雞好難做<br />\n先唔講佢d 員工執餐執到咁撚慢<br />\n堂食你又開得唔夠多鋪 山長水遠起碼行十幾廿分鐘先買到黎食 想拎返屋企佢又唔夠脆<br />\n外賣又係同一個問題 黎到都已經唔好食 <br />\n仲有個價又高過m記 有時想食炸雞 不如買個脆香雞翼算<br />\nKFC 如果唔出多d 包同飯類再降低d 個價 佢應該會愈執愈多"},{"pid":"1af6350ccec854c86a9044535a02fa8a52496d9f","tid":444461,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:04:05.000Z","msg":"另外依家咁多人講求健康 都小左好多人會考慮買炸雞食<br />\n就算食都係食m記 睇起上黎比較炸雞叫冇咁油膩咁高卡路里"},{"pid":"affc0a41ca16369ba934d954ac85ebd6ff483045","tid":444461,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港KFC啲人做嘢慢過龜<br />\n唔使專登拉長營業時間都可以開足24小時</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑左出聲"},{"pid":"a7bf447e824de484588bc1e992093c97628a90aa","tid":444461,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌，我住左十幾年我果區都未開24小時m記。。。</blockquote><br />\n好少可wo 港島區？</blockquote><br />\n孤島</blockquote><br />\n真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果真 咁應該有排都唔會有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梅窩？</blockquote><br />\n唔自爆la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n海怡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f82a707eed0809f82394826d748822a164836d","tid":444461,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:09:56.000Z","msg":"其實最大問題係佢d 炸雞一定要堂食先好味 除非你屋企同kfc 好近 但係kfc 分店咁小 得好小人係近kfc<br />\n當d 炸雞一唔好食 大家想叫雞既心情就冷卻曬 <br />\n可能你話kfc 有包有飯 但係我叫包 不如叫個m記 叫飯我不如叫pizza hut 仲有埋意粉<br />\n所以我勸kfc 推出多d 品種既包同飯類或者加埋意粉 咁佢就唔駛執笠 <br />\n當kfc 可以有能力開返多d 鋪既時候先主打炸雞喇 因為開多左鋪即係好大機會你樓下5分鐘路程有一間kfc 到時叫拎走 或外賣 d 雞都唔會淋左唔好食喇"},{"pid":"26159da49185156196a4cd0621c188e503509ae9","tid":444461,"uid":99642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:19:51.000Z","msg":"我覺得KFC宜家做得幾好<br />\n<br />\n市場個邊做得幾好"},{"pid":"9917a6c077de7f561dd69d72773e85f6152c3b26","tid":444461,"uid":99642,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港KFC感覺愈做愈霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出左D飯,茶餐,早餐之後我覺得好左<br />\n<br />\n比10年前好我覺得"},{"pid":"aaf7a43c7a1afe1022dcf67449a45c5864b538ec","tid":444461,"uid":123248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港KFC感覺愈做愈霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國kfc 其實都好霉<br />\n唔好怪香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6546ede7ec803751d1f961ba381b0a059126e4e0","tid":444461,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:52:37.000Z","msg":"唔知你地知唔知香港勞工法418 個rule ? <br />\n幾年前仲係咁，唔知而家係咪<br />\nKfc full time 員工都唔會比佢地過418， 咁樣比少好多錢（員工福利同大假唔洗比），咁刻薄，點會肯開24"},{"pid":"383faa46110487e4bbf49317ee9f1c011109d753","tid":444461,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T21:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港KFC感覺愈做愈霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國kfc 其實都好霉<br />\n唔好怪香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國太多對手 不過kfc 的確愈做d 雞水準愈低 比其他炸雞店超越左好耐"}]}